checkers.types.visitors

Class AnnotatedTypeComparer<R extends @Nullable Object>

  • @Nullable java.lang.Object
    • checkers.types.visitors.AnnotatedTypeScanner<R,@Mutable AnnotatedTypeMirror>
      • checkers.types.visitors.AnnotatedTypeComparer<R>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotatedTypeVisitor<R,@Mutable AnnotatedTypeMirror>

    public class AnnotatedTypeComparer<R extends @Nullable Object>
extends AnnotatedTypeScanner<R,@Mutable AnnotatedTypeMirror>
    A TypeVisitor that takes an AnnotatedTypeMirror as a parameter, and visits it simultaneously. Note that the parameter type must be assignable to the visited type, or an assertion fails when visiting an incompatible subtype.
    See Also:
    AnnotatedTypeScanner
